1
00:00:00,528 --> 00:00:08,628
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,803 --> 00:00:17,040
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,278 --> 00:00:19,269
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,283 --> 00:00:26,049
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:29,487
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,690 --> 00:00:33,251
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,627 --> 00:00:36,994
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,064 --> 00:00:44,493
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,572 --> 00:00:53,708
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,781 --> 00:01:01,813
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,056 --> 00:01:08,894
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,963 --> 00:01:17,029
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,338 --> 00:01:25,803
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:27,905
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:44,042 --> 00:01:46,272
<i>His opponent is that Neji, huh...?</i>

16
00:01:46,711 --> 00:01:49,441
<i>The Final Round is altogether different</i>
<i>than the preliminaries...</i>

17
00:01:49,981 --> 00:01:51,676
<i>After all, Naruto may not be able to...</i>

18
00:02:11,269 --> 00:02:15,171
Entertain me a little, Naruto.

19
00:02:16,641 --> 00:02:20,771
I've got a tough job waiting
for me now, so...

20
00:02:22,414 --> 00:02:28,375
<i>Ultimate Defense. Zero Blind Spot!</i>

21
00:03:01,953 --> 00:03:04,581
Dang it. I can't catch him at all.

22
00:03:07,192 --> 00:03:09,820
I told you I'm not
such a fool, didn't I?

23
00:03:17,002 --> 00:03:21,029
<i>I already know...</i>
<i>which one is the real one.</i>

24
00:03:27,279 --> 00:03:27,904
Oh.

25
00:03:28,346 --> 00:03:31,076
That is the body
that has least attacks

26
00:03:31,149 --> 00:03:34,016
due to its fear of having
Chakra Points attacked.

27
00:03:34,352 --> 00:03:36,718
The more you attack,

28
00:03:36,788 --> 00:03:38,756
the more that one body
becomes clearly evident.

29
00:03:42,527 --> 00:03:44,222
You're the real one.

30
00:03:44,562 --> 00:03:45,654
Naruto...

31
00:03:46,197 --> 00:03:47,528
This is as far as it goes.

32
00:03:52,570 --> 00:03:54,470
I said it was pointless.

33
00:03:57,409 --> 00:03:59,843
Don't let him beat you, Naruto.

34
00:04:04,716 --> 00:04:09,517
I've been telling you not
to frivolously assume things.

35
00:04:11,189 --> 00:04:11,780
What?

36
00:04:12,691 --> 00:04:13,521
It can't be.

37
00:04:19,064 --> 00:04:21,794
All right! Go, Naruto!

38
00:04:23,168 --> 00:04:24,066
Naruto!

39
00:04:24,803 --> 00:04:29,672
<i>He foiled my idea and purposely</i>
<i>and drew one of his clones back?</i>

40
00:04:30,308 --> 00:04:34,642
I've been striking from the beginning,
prepared for an honorable death!

41
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:35,573
Believe it!

42
00:04:37,248 --> 00:04:37,737
<i>I did it.</i>

43
00:04:44,989 --> 00:04:45,819
That's...

44
00:04:59,738 --> 00:05:02,104
W-What was that?

45
00:05:03,274 --> 00:05:05,174
Did you think you'd won?

46
00:05:07,679 --> 00:05:08,611
Why?

47
00:05:08,813 --> 00:05:10,974
Naruto's punch should've hit.

48
00:05:12,283 --> 00:05:13,409
That...

49
00:05:17,889 --> 00:05:19,322
Rotation...

50
00:05:23,294 --> 00:05:25,285
<i>That's Neji's defense.</i>

51
00:05:27,198 --> 00:05:29,962
You punk.
Don't make a fool of me.

52
00:05:34,339 --> 00:05:38,435
The largest range of vision of
Neji's Byakugan is nearly 360 degrees.

53
00:05:39,511 --> 00:05:43,003
And he detects all of his opponent's
attacks with the Byakugan.

54
00:05:45,383 --> 00:05:48,375
His defense technique,
the 8 Trigrams Palms Rotation,

55
00:05:48,453 --> 00:05:49,442
will begin from here.

56
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:12,698
The moment he's attacked,
he discharges a large amount of Chakra

57
00:06:12,777 --> 00:06:16,907
from the Chakra holes in the body,
blocks the enemy's attack with that Chakra,

58
00:06:16,981 --> 00:06:21,111
moves his own body in a circular motion,
dodges and repels.

59
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:26,754
Essentially, it's difficult to control
the Chakra discharged from Chakra holes...

60
00:06:27,225 --> 00:06:30,683
To the extent that even Jonin utilize
the discharge from a part of the body,

61
00:06:30,762 --> 00:06:32,593
like the hands and feet,
in techniques.

62
00:06:33,665 --> 00:06:37,192
But Neji who has mastered
Gentle Fist discharges Chakra

63
00:06:37,268 --> 00:06:40,431
from his entire body and
shuts out physical attacks

64
00:06:40,505 --> 00:06:42,336
just with that discharge power.

65
00:06:43,675 --> 00:06:44,903
In other words,

66
00:06:44,976 --> 00:06:47,843
that's one more absolute defense

67
00:06:47,912 --> 00:06:50,813
that has more power
than that Gaara's Sand Shield.

68
00:06:57,222 --> 00:06:59,281
T-That's father's...

69
00:06:59,357 --> 00:07:02,451
The Rotation is a secret Art passed down
from generation to generation

70
00:07:02,527 --> 00:07:05,894
only to the Hyuga head family,
in other words the Hyuga clan.

71
00:07:06,865 --> 00:07:09,265
He created that on his own?

72
00:07:09,901 --> 00:07:13,098
He's quite the guy...
To think he'd come this far.

73
00:07:14,606 --> 00:07:19,475
<i>It's much too soon to be surprised.</i>
<i>Neji's true power is still to come.</i>

74
00:07:20,912 --> 00:07:22,106
Dang it.

75
00:07:22,647 --> 00:07:24,171
This is the end.

76
00:07:25,683 --> 00:07:29,141
You're within the area of my 8 Trigrams.

77
00:07:40,665 --> 00:07:42,530
Gentle Fist Art.

78
00:07:43,501 --> 00:07:45,560
8 Trigrams 64 Palms.

79
00:07:46,137 --> 00:07:47,001
It can't be.

80
00:07:47,272 --> 00:07:48,364
That pose.

81
00:07:57,115 --> 00:07:58,241
8 Tetragrams...

82
00:07:59,384 --> 00:08:00,112
...2 Palms!

83
00:08:03,621 --> 00:08:04,485
4 Palms.

84
00:08:06,057 --> 00:08:06,955
8 Palms.

85
00:08:08,693 --> 00:08:09,660
16 Palms.

86
00:08:11,062 --> 00:08:12,256
32 Palms.

87
00:08:15,166 --> 00:08:17,134
64 Palms!

88
00:08:22,073 --> 00:08:24,871
<i>The branch family exceeds</i>
<i>the head family?</i>

89
00:08:38,856 --> 00:08:40,221
It's over.

90
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:48,528
<i>Truly a terrifying talent.</i>

91
00:08:49,067 --> 00:08:51,627
<i>To think the power of the</i>
<i>Hyuga Kekkei Genkai</i>

92
00:08:51,703 --> 00:08:54,900
<i>would be passed on so strongly</i>
<i>to a child of the branch family</i>

93
00:08:54,973 --> 00:08:57,908
<i>who would never be able</i>
<i>to be an heir.</i>

94
00:08:59,577 --> 00:09:04,071
<i>Hizashi... You should have</i>
<i>succeeded the Hyuga family.</i>

95
00:09:05,149 --> 00:09:08,585
I pressed the 64 Chakra Points
all over your body...

96
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,745
You can't even stand.

97
00:09:14,158 --> 00:09:15,455
D-Dang it.

98
00:09:16,961 --> 00:09:18,292
Are you frustrated?

99
00:09:18,563 --> 00:09:21,327
Kneeling down before power
that can't be changed

100
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:23,196
and knowing your powerlessness.

101
00:09:24,268 --> 00:09:27,567
Your dreams will come true
if you just work hard.

102
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:29,072
That's just an illusion.

103
00:09:31,542 --> 00:09:33,874
Hey, Hinata. Are you okay?

104
00:09:34,145 --> 00:09:36,579
Oh, man. I knew it.

105
00:09:36,648 --> 00:09:37,706
Naruto.

106
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:10,145
<i>Bushy brow...</i>

107
00:10:12,917 --> 00:10:13,941
<i>Hinata.</i>

108
00:10:21,192 --> 00:10:22,750
D-Dang it.

109
00:10:24,662 --> 00:10:25,390
Oh.

110
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:33,368
Naruto.

111
00:10:44,315 --> 00:10:47,648
He... No way.

112
00:10:49,654 --> 00:10:51,212
I told you, didn't I...?

113
00:10:51,789 --> 00:10:55,691
I don't know when to give up.

114
00:11:06,271 --> 00:11:07,465
No way.

115
00:11:09,741 --> 00:11:12,403
Hey, you're bleeding

116
00:11:12,911 --> 00:11:13,900
What's wrong?

117
00:11:14,813 --> 00:11:18,078
You've still got damage
from the match.

118
00:11:19,418 --> 00:11:21,409
Hinata... Hang in there.

119
00:11:27,025 --> 00:11:28,219
I'll take a look at her.

120
00:11:29,695 --> 00:11:30,719
Who're you?

121
00:11:31,697 --> 00:11:33,892
I'm not suspicious or anything.

122
00:11:35,033 --> 00:11:36,466
Stop already...

123
00:11:36,768 --> 00:11:38,702
It'll be the same even if
you fight more than this.

124
00:11:39,004 --> 00:11:40,938
I don't have a grudge particularly
against you.

125
00:11:41,673 --> 00:11:43,106
S-Shut up...

126
00:11:43,675 --> 00:11:47,202
Even if you say so,
I have something against you.

127
00:11:47,479 --> 00:11:48,741
What are you talking about?

128
00:11:49,214 --> 00:11:53,514
Why...? Here you're this strong...

129
00:11:54,086 --> 00:11:57,487
Why did you, with a look like
you've seen through it all,

130
00:11:57,556 --> 00:12:03,119
go after Hinata mentally
who was trying so hard?

131
00:12:03,996 --> 00:12:06,556
It has nothing to do with you.

132
00:12:07,165 --> 00:12:11,761
Mocking Hinata, selfishly labeling
her a failure as you please.

133
00:12:12,037 --> 00:12:13,868
Head family, branch family...

134
00:12:13,939 --> 00:12:16,806
I don't know what happened to you.

135
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:23,548
But I won't forgive the jerk who'd
call another person a failure.

136
00:12:29,021 --> 00:12:30,318
Hey, you.

137
00:12:30,522 --> 00:12:32,854
It's okay. I'm a doctor.

138
00:12:34,626 --> 00:12:37,151
Okay... Fine.

139
00:12:37,329 --> 00:12:42,562
If you insist, I'll tell you about
the Hyuga's destiny of hatred.

140
00:12:44,803 --> 00:12:46,771
In the Hyuga head family,
there's a secret Ninjutsu

141
00:12:46,838 --> 00:12:48,703
that's been passed on
from generation to generation.

142
00:12:49,708 --> 00:12:51,198
That is the Curse Mark Arts.

143
00:12:52,678 --> 00:12:54,009
Curse Mark Arts?

144
00:12:59,518 --> 00:13:03,215
The Curse Mark represents
a bird in a cage...

145
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:08,221
and it's a mark of those who are
bound to a destiny they can't escape.

146
00:13:21,740 --> 00:13:23,037
W-What's...

147
00:13:34,586 --> 00:13:36,110
...t-that mark?

148
00:13:37,556 --> 00:13:39,353
One day when I was four years old,

149
00:13:39,424 --> 00:13:44,487
this accursed mark was inscribed
on my forehead with the Curse Mark Arts.

150
00:13:47,032 --> 00:13:51,230
A large ceremony was held in
the Village Hidden in Leaves on that day.

151
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:55,101
It was also the day when the
head Ninja of the Land of Lightning,

152
00:13:55,173 --> 00:13:57,437
the land that the Leaf had
fought with for many years,

153
00:13:57,509 --> 00:14:01,036
came for the conclusion
of the allied treaty.

154
00:14:02,881 --> 00:14:05,349
However, there was one clan...

155
00:14:05,417 --> 00:14:07,783
who didn't attend the ceremony
that was attended

156
00:14:07,853 --> 00:14:10,788
by everybody else,
from Leaf Jonin to Genin.

157
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:13,624
It was the Hyuga clan...

158
00:14:14,493 --> 00:14:16,586
And it's because that day
was the day of hope

159
00:14:16,661 --> 00:14:19,027
when the head family heir
was to turn three.

160
00:14:21,867 --> 00:14:24,392
Miss Hinata's third birthday!

161
00:14:37,582 --> 00:14:39,812
My father, Hizashi Hyuga,

162
00:14:39,885 --> 00:14:44,720
and Miss Hinata's father who's over there,
Lord Hiashi Hyuga, were twin brothers.

163
00:14:46,091 --> 00:14:49,151
However, Miss Hinata's father,
Lord Hiashi,

164
00:14:49,227 --> 00:14:53,027
is the eldest son of the head family
born into this world first.

165
00:14:53,965 --> 00:14:57,662
And my father who was the second son
is a member of the branch family.

166
00:14:59,938 --> 00:15:02,207
<i>So Miss Hinata is already three...</i>

167
00:15:02,207 --> 00:15:03,640
<i>Congratulations.</i>

168
00:15:04,076 --> 00:15:04,701
<i>Thank you.</i>

169
00:15:13,418 --> 00:15:15,909
<i>She's a cute girl, isn't she, father?</i>

170
00:15:21,393 --> 00:15:23,827
<i>What's wrong, father?</i>

171
00:15:25,163 --> 00:15:27,290
<i>Oh, it's nothing.</i>

172
00:15:29,434 --> 00:15:30,423
<i>Then...</i>

173
00:15:30,836 --> 00:15:33,202
<i>I'll be taking Neji under my care, Hizashi.</i>

174
00:15:33,638 --> 00:15:34,434
<i>Yes.</i>

175
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:39,073
When the head family heir grew
and became three years old,

176
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:45,280
I had the Curse Mark imprinted on me
and I became the bird in the cage.

177
00:15:45,917 --> 00:15:47,475
And became the Hyuga branch family.

178
00:15:47,552 --> 00:15:50,077
Why's it necessary to do
something like that?

179
00:15:50,455 --> 00:15:53,219
Why separate into a head family
and a branch family?

180
00:15:53,525 --> 00:15:56,790
What does that weird mark mean?

181
00:15:57,062 --> 00:16:00,725
This mark on my forehead
isn't just a decoration.

182
00:16:10,142 --> 00:16:11,837
<i>The pull of your legs is weak.</i>

183
00:16:11,910 --> 00:16:12,706
<i>Yes.</i>

184
00:16:20,051 --> 00:16:21,313
<i>Listen, Neji.</i>

185
00:16:21,386 --> 00:16:25,482
<i>You will live to protect Miss Hinata</i>
<i>of the head family</i>

186
00:16:25,557 --> 00:16:28,390
<i>as well as the Hyuga power.</i>

187
00:16:29,227 --> 00:16:30,717
<i>Yes, father.</i>

188
00:16:52,851 --> 00:16:53,613
<i>Murderous Intent.</i>

189
00:17:01,927 --> 00:17:03,019
<i>My head.</i>

190
00:17:03,094 --> 00:17:03,958
<i>Father.</i>

191
00:17:07,465 --> 00:17:08,796
<i>What's wrong, father?</i>

192
00:17:10,001 --> 00:17:14,961
<i>Go home.</i>
<i>I'll forgive the fool today only.</i>

193
00:17:16,174 --> 00:17:19,075
<i>You're not to forget your destiny.</i>

194
00:17:23,782 --> 00:17:27,013
This Curse Mark is the absolute fear
called death so to speak...

195
00:17:27,085 --> 00:17:29,417
that was given to the branch family
by the head family.

196
00:17:31,523 --> 00:17:33,582
The Secret Sign that the
head family members form easily

197
00:17:33,658 --> 00:17:36,957
destroys the cerebral nerves
of those in the branch family.

198
00:17:37,796 --> 00:17:40,264
Of course, killing is easy.

199
00:17:41,066 --> 00:17:45,002
And this mark only goes away
at time of death.

200
00:17:46,137 --> 00:17:48,503
Sealing away the power
of the Byakugan.

201
00:17:53,278 --> 00:17:57,078
The Hyuga family is the clan that possesses
the most distinctive Kekkei Genkai.

202
00:17:58,083 --> 00:18:01,382
There's no end to those who
target the secret of that distinctive power.

203
00:18:03,321 --> 00:18:07,724
In other words, this Curse Mark
keeps the branch family alive

204
00:18:07,792 --> 00:18:11,159
only to protect the head family
and does not allow disobedience.

205
00:18:11,363 --> 00:18:15,629
And it's an effective system created
to defend for eternity

206
00:18:15,700 --> 00:18:18,066
the Kekkei Genkai called Byakugan.

207
00:18:18,436 --> 00:18:22,873
And then, that incident occurred.

208
00:18:24,109 --> 00:18:29,012
My father was killed by
the head family.

209
00:18:33,051 --> 00:18:36,748
One night, Miss Hinata was
snatched up by someone.

210
00:19:02,914 --> 00:19:06,873
At that time, Lord Hiashi immediately
rushed off and killed the abductor.

211
00:19:08,086 --> 00:19:11,078
Who do you think that person was...

212
00:19:11,156 --> 00:19:15,354
who was in the shadows,
and also wearing a mask?

213
00:19:16,394 --> 00:19:20,296
It was the head ninja of
the Land of Lightning

214
00:19:20,365 --> 00:19:23,095
who had just completed
the allied treaty.

215
00:19:23,702 --> 00:19:27,661
It was clear that he came targeting
the secret of Byakugan from the start.

216
00:19:28,606 --> 00:19:32,542
However, the Land of Lightning
exploited the killing of their own Ninja

217
00:19:32,610 --> 00:19:34,168
due to a botched plan...

218
00:19:34,245 --> 00:19:39,012
and set an outrageous condition in
violation of the treaty with the Hidden Leaf.

219
00:19:45,290 --> 00:19:47,281
Naturally, things got worse and worse,

220
00:19:47,359 --> 00:19:49,827
and there was almost a war
between the Leaf and the Lightning.

221
00:19:51,262 --> 00:19:53,628
However, the Leaf who
wanted to avoid war

222
00:19:53,698 --> 00:19:55,529
made a deal with the Lightning.

223
00:19:56,401 --> 00:19:57,561
A deal?

224
00:19:58,503 --> 00:20:00,664
The Lightning demand was
the body of the Hyuga head family

225
00:20:00,739 --> 00:20:03,572
who possesses Byakugan,
the Kekkei Genkai...

226
00:20:04,642 --> 00:20:08,373
In other words,
the body of Lord Hiashi.

227
00:20:10,982 --> 00:20:13,746
And the Leaf accepted the condition.

228
00:20:14,252 --> 00:20:16,584
<i>What? But, father...</i>

229
00:20:17,489 --> 00:20:20,515
And war was safely avoided.

230
00:20:21,793 --> 00:20:27,663
Thanks to my father who was killed
as a body double of Hiashi Hyuga,

231
00:20:27,732 --> 00:20:29,893
to protect the head family!

232
00:20:30,735 --> 00:20:35,229
Other than dying, there's no other way
to escape this accursed Curse Mark.

233
00:20:36,374 --> 00:20:39,537
Even though they were twins
with nearly equal power,

234
00:20:39,611 --> 00:20:45,072
their destinies were already set by
who was born first and born later.

235
00:20:51,156 --> 00:20:52,680
And then, this match...

236
00:20:53,291 --> 00:20:57,660
Your destiny was decided at the point
when I became your opponent.

237
00:21:12,211 --> 00:21:15,578
<i>One! First, Tyson jumps and slamdunks</i>

238
00:21:15,648 --> 00:21:18,981
<i>Two! He kisses and hugs everyone</i>
<i>randomly and says "I LOVE YOU"</i>

239
00:21:19,051 --> 00:21:22,487
<i>Three! Masala masters Yoga</i>
